description: Sensodyne Sensitive Care Soft Toothbrush is specially designed for people with sensitive teeth. With 2.5 times better pressure control (1), this manual toothbrush cleans better with less pressure (2). Featuring a DuoFlex neck, this gentle toothbrush is designed to reach hard-to-clean areas. This Sensodyne toothbrush pack contains a total of four toothbrushes, giving you plenty to stock your bathroom, travel kit, office and more with oral care products. It is recommended that toothbrushes are replaced every 3 months. For optimum treatment of tooth sensitivity, brush twice daily using Sensodyne toothpaste. Get lasting protection from tooth sensitivity with Sensodyne. (1) Versus standard neck in laboratory testing, (2) In laboratory tests compared to a standard flat-trim toothbrush.
